  "title": "Business Information Analayst #ESY",
  "description": "<p>•\tSupport Deployment Principal to communicate, onboard, and support suppliers in execution of Product Traceability Compliance programs using Deployment principal approved messaging</p><p>•\tDevelop and optimize APIs and SQL queries for efficient data extraction on a biweekly basis</p><p>•\tCreate and maintain interactive dashboards using Excel and Tableau / Power BI</p><p>•\tImplement and manage data ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) processes</p><p>•\tCollaborate with platform vendors to ensure data accuracy and accessibility</p><p>•\tDevelop reports to present insights and recommendations to stakeholders</p><p>•\tMonitor function email inbox, escalate to appropriate teams and respond directly per guidance</p><p>•\tDevelop and maintain communication calendar and deployment timeline</p><p>•\tMeeting scheduling, notes, and recaps</p><p>•\tDocument and maintain program FAQs and responses</p><p>•\tDevelop, deploy, and analyze supplier survey on program feedback</p><p>•\tPerform validations in product traceability platform as needed per guidance (e.g., supplier requests to delete incoming transactions)</p><p><br /><br />Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
